@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "Pure LLM (Stateless)" as LLMBox #E8F0FE {
  [User Prompt] as Prompt #BBDEFB
  [LLM Inference] as Inference #BBDEFB
  [Text Response] as Response #BBDEFB
  Prompt -down-> Inference
  Inference -down-> Response
}

note left of LLMBox
  **Limitations**
  --
  - No memory across turns
  - No ability to act
  - No access to tools/APIs
  - No file system access
  - Hallucinates when
    knowledge is stale
  - Single-shot output only
end note

package "Agent Framework (Orchestrated)" as AgentBox #E8F5E9 {
  [User Request] as Req #C8E6C9

  package "Agent Loop (Perceive > Think > Act)" #DCEDC8 {
    [LLM\n(The Brain)] as Brain #BBDEFB
    [Tool Execution\n(Read, Write, Bash, API)] as Tools #FFF9C4
    [Session & Memory\n(Context Persistence)] as Memory #F3E5F5

    Brain <--> Tools : results / calls
    Brain <--> Memory : context / persist
  }

  [Final Response\n+ Side Effects] as Final #C8E6C9

  Req --> Brain
  Brain --> Final
}

note right of AgentBox
  **What the Agent Adds**
  --
  - Persistent memory
  - Tool use (real actions)
  - Multi-turn reasoning
  - Error recovery & retry
  - Security boundaries
  - Session management
end note

LLMBox -[hidden]right- AgentBox
@enduml
